== :::Phonogram::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::: ==
'''Phonogram''' is an artistic, multimedia project of '''Lukas Balaz'''. Under this label he releases his production.

This project is a pseudodipteral for personal expression through the art, music, writing, etc. Mostly using the digital sources for presentation such as internet. The goal of this project is to create the complex multimedia format. Lukas Balaz also joins the [[Make Poverty History]] campaign.

